Package: badger
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian approach for detecting copy number alterations from single cell RNA-seq data
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-10-18
Author: Jean Fan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jean Fan <jeanfan@fas.harvard.edu>
Description: The badger package implements a set of statistical methods for inferring copy number alterations and loss of heterozygosity events from single-cell RNA-seq data.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
